Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.75,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It looks like another\N﻿murder happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.12,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿They say every\N﻿victim is a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're the one who\N﻿should be careful, Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.10,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Especially when you go out at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.24,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.81,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't go out a lot at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I just haven't the time lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.01,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.61,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.69,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have this new private teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.42,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.59,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.59,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:35.73,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Anyway, he's tall, handsome, and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.73,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:08.97,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.44,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.81,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Next stop is the private school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.65,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The private school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.61,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.65,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A strange man holding a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.25,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please be careful as you step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.76,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:35.96,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:49.81,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.01,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.07,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.91,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're always so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.76,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Azusa, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're talking about this stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.58,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Remember when we\N﻿went to Karuizawa last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.21,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I picked it up then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.53,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.53,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Everybody's gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Well, can you give me this stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:29.77,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's just something I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But why do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.88,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm just kind of interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:44.35,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's not just an ornament, there's\N﻿something mysterious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:49.42,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I always feel relaxed when\N﻿I look into a beautiful stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.52,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Oh, I have a pretty stone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.26,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.79,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.60,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.80,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿W-Wait a moment, Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.77,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.95,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry, I have to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.58,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Okay, take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.25,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I didn't expect it to take this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.35,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It was that cat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.66,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I was asked a lot of\N﻿questions by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:19.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:23.10,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Of course, I told them everything I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:37.38,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But they said the\N﻿cat didn't kill anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.05,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I think that man did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:45.52,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Remember, yesterday he\N﻿was in the bus watching us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.86,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The cat he held was the\N﻿same cat I saw last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm positive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.37,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.37,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:11.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you thinking about a guy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:15.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I told you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My private teacher is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm thinking about seducing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.92,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.15,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You come here to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, this is my\N﻿private teacher, Mr. Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is my friend, Miho Murakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.43,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The bus is too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.00,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Jeez, aren't I attractive enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.51,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:25.88,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.42,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You picked up a beautiful\N﻿stone at Karuizawa, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.26,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.52,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:41.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please think about it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A pretty stone at Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.44,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A pretty stone that shines blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Come to think of it, I\N﻿remember something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.21,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Where could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.25,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.56,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.89,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.93,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Then where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:35.55,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's sit on the sofa and talk about It.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.89,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Well, Mr. Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.19,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿about the stone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.19,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.86,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:54.93,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In return...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.44,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,...﻿would you do what I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,...﻿Mr. Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.69,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mr. Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.47,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, you're so hard already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:45.99,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.94,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mr. inoue, please lick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.37,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.94,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.01,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I-I gave it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I gave it to Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:06.03,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I-I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:25.64,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mr. Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:42.80,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:26.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:03.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:27.23,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.10,0:24:31.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's the sex beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.94,0:24:36.01,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He killed Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:36.90,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.77,0:26:10.80,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:12.77,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.94,0:26:46.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mr. Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.34,0:26:49.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.68,0:26:52.31,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mr. Inoue, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.45,0:26:53.48,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.97,0:27:13.23,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.71,0:27:26.41,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.65,0:27:32.22,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:35.62,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He is looking for the Dark Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.96,0:27:37.09,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Dark Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.69,0:27:39.89,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Stone you got from Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:46.43,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He approached Azusa\N﻿and tried to take the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.73,0:27:49.77,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And, he killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.78,0:27:59.41,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You have the Dark Stone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.32,0:28:08.55,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I need it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.13,0:28:48.00,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.03,0:28:51.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Finally, I have the Dark Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.64,0:30:37.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.37,0:30:39.81,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.51,0:30:43.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You killed Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.18,0:30:45.48,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.58,0:30:49.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.88,0:30:53.65,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I didn't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.99,0:30:56.32,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're the sex beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.56,0:30:58.69,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:06.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes. I'm a sex beast,\N﻿but I didn't kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.90,0:31:10.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You saw, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.64,0:31:12.34,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Inoue's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.61,0:31:16.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's a sex beast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.94,0:31:18.88,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I was chasing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.32,0:31:25.92,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I came here to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.03,0:31:41.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It wasn't you who killed Azusa, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.97,0:31:47.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You aren't the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.31,0:31:49.88,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No, he is the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.34,0:31:53.51,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Then why was that\N﻿cat always at the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.55,0:31:57.82,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Because I have been chasing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.89,0:32:06.79,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sex beasts have taken human\N﻿energy to survive for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.30,0:32:11.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But we never kill human beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.33,0:32:21.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿...because we would die\N﻿if our food source died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.08,0:32:26.61,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We have co-existed with you always...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.25,0:32:35.02,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿However, now there is a special\N﻿sex beast, whose aim is to kill humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.86,0:32:41.13,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have to kill him for our race.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.86,0:32:47.47,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have to take back the stone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.50,0:32:50.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What is the stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.47,0:32:56.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That stone is the Dark Stone,\N﻿handed down for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.88,0:32:58.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Dark Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.48,0:33:04.85,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Dark Stone\N﻿gives us unlimited power.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.99,0:33:11.76,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He tried to get the\N﻿stone when it was sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.80,0:33:21.70,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I got in his way, and we began to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.00,0:33:56.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to take back the Dark Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.51,0:34:07.38,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We couldn't approach because it\N﻿was protected by a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.55,0:34:11.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It was the power of the Bright Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.65,0:34:18.19,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Bright Stone is\N﻿dangerous, because it can kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.73,0:34:27.30,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So, he couldn't approach Azusa\N﻿easily because he was afraid of the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.07,0:34:32.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But, she was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.31,0:34:36.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿She didn't have the Bright Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.61,0:34:41.71,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The person who has the stone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.45,0:34:45.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.45,0:34:50.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿At that time, only you were near Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.66,0:34:52.66,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.06,0:34:54.86,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Bright Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.50,0:34:56.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.06,0:34:58.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You must have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.12,0:35:21.79,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There is a stone in my charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.26,0:35:23.29,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.46,0:35:26.13,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In my pouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.86,0:35:29.09,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Shit, now he has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.70,0:35:34.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.70,0:35:36.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's in my locker from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.34,0:35:37.34,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You left it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.57,0:35:38.27,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.47,0:35:39.34,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.30,0:36:07.33,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.55,0:36:29.66,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We can get rid of him with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.66,0:36:30.62,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.59,0:36:33.99,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can avenge Azusa, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.03,0:36:34.86,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.96,0:36:38.56,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.67,0:36:39.60,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have to hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.73,0:36:41.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.10,0:36:44.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.04,0:37:21.91,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:44.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Finally, I have unlimited power!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.97,0:37:55.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.45,0:38:03.62,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.23,0:38:13.43,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:16.53,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.17,0:38:56.34,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.60,0:39:00.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thanks to you, I could\N﻿take revenge for Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:01.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.21,0:39:06.48,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I've reached the end of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.68,0:39:08.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.08,0:39:10.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.29,0:39:21.09,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.23,0:39:23.66,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you take my energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.43,0:39:27.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.00,0:39:32.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're a sex beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.07,0:39:37.31,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,...﻿but you fought for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.15,0:39:50.19,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is the one thing I can do for you.